title: The Pinball Arcade v1.26.12 to v1.27.2
description:
HOW TO PATCH v1.26.12 to v1.27.2

1. Copy the contents from the folder "v1.26.12 - Original Files" REPLACE FILES into the game folder 
2. Copy "TPA - v1.26.12 to v1.27.2" into the game folder
3. Run as Admin "TPA - v1.26.12 to v1.27.2" and click "YES"
4. Wait for the patcher to finish (it takes several minutes)
5. Copy the contents from the folder "v1.27.2 - Crack Files" into the game folder
6. Enjoy

The folder "v1.27.2 - Original Files" is included for future patches.


I hope you have great times with this amazing game.
